CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...center, left to right; Mae Bailey, Boston; Pauline Davis, Boston...- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Mae Bailey and Pauline Davis wearing hat, posed on Loendi Club porch for Debs About Town conference
